8 An Act relating to animals; defining terms; exempting
certain individuals and entities from provisions;
9 requiring certain authorization; prohibiting certain
amount of chanticleers to be kept; prohibiting
10 provisions from preventing current enforcement;
providing penalties; allowing the Oklahoma Department
11 of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry to cooperate with
certain entities; providing for promulgation of
12 rules; amending 21 O.S. 2021, Section 1692.9, which
relates to cockfighting prohibition exemptions;
13 adding exemption; updating statutory reference;
providing for codification; and providing an
14 effective date.
